{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Network Information API","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>這是一個實驗中的功能</strong><br>此功能在某些瀏覽器尚在開發中，請參考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">兼容表格</a>以得到不同瀏覽器用的前輟。</p></div><p></p>\n<p>Network Information API 將提供系統連線的相關資訊，如使用者裝置的現有頻寬，或目前的連線狀態。根據使用者的連線情形，可進一步選擇高解析度或低解析度的內容。此完整的 API 另包含 domxref(\"Connection\") 介面，以及 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> 介面的單一屬性 ─ <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/connection\"><code>Navigator.connection</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"偵測連線變化","title":"偵測連線變化","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此範例將觀察使用者連線的變化。舉例來說，當使用者從高價位連線轉用低價位連線時，就會降低頻寬需求以避免連線費用暴增，並採用類似 Apps 受到警示的方法。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> connection <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>connection <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mozConnection <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>webkitConnection<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">updateConnectionStatus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Connection bandwidth: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> connection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bandwidth <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" MB/s\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>connection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>metered<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"The connection is metered!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconnection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"change\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> updateConnectionStatus<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">updateConnectionStatus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"規範","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"query":"api.NetworkInformation,api.Navigator.connection","specifications":[]}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://wicg.github.io/netinfo/#connection-attribute","title":"Network Information API"}],"query":"api.Navigator.connection"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"瀏覽器相容性","title":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"NetworkInformation","id":"networkinformation","isH3":true,"data":null,"query":"api.NetworkInformation,api.Navigator.connection","browsers":null}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Navigator.connection","id":"navigator.connection","isH3":true,"query":"api.Navigator.connection","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/dap/raw-file/tip/network-api/Overview.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Network Information API Specification</a><span title=\"Editor's Draft (unofficial)\" style=\"color:#fff;background:#e61919;display:inline-block; font-size:x-small; margin-left:6px; white-space:nowrap; padding:2px 5px;\">ED</span></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Online_and_offline_events\">線上與離線事件</a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>window.navigator.connection</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"偵測連線變化","id":"偵測連線變化"},{"text":"規範","id":"specifications"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Network Information API 將提供系統連線的相關資訊，如使用者裝置的現有頻寬，或目前的連線狀態。根據使用者的連線情形，可進一步選擇高解析度或低解析度的內容。此完整的 API 另包含 domxref(\"Connection\") 介面，以及 Navigator 介面的單一屬性 ─ Navigator.connection。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"网络状况 API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/network_information_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translate